items.title: JD Martinez first 4-time Player of the Week
items.summary: The National and American Leagues have awarded Player of the Week honors since 1974. Never before has any player done enough to earn so many in a season as J.D. Martinez has this year.

items.title: Scoreless streak wins Kluber AL Player of Week
items.summary: Corey Kluber continues to be automatic every five days for an Indians team that just went on a historic 22-game win streak, and after two more brilliant outings, the Cleveland ace took home the American League Player of the Week Award on Monday.
